&lt;p>Participation is highly recommended (especially for for PhD and MSc students), but optional. For more information, have a look at the &lt;a href="https://acmrecsys.github.io/rsss2019/recsys_summerschool_tutorassignment.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">assignment&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We kindly ask you to sign up via the following &lt;a href="https://forms.gle/caQeMZqHZVQs1k1B8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google form&lt;/a> before Sunday, 8 September, 21h, as we will need some time to plan the sessions.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Speaker at RecSys Summer School 2019</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-01-speaker-at-recsys-summer-school-2019/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2019 22:45:08 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2019-07-01-speaker-at-recsys-summer-school-2019/</guid><description>&lt;p>I am happy to be a speaker at the &lt;a href="https://acmrecsys.github.io/rsss2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ACM Summer School on Recommender Systems&lt;/a> taking place in Gothenburg, Sweden, just a week before the official &lt;a href="https://recsys.acm.org/recsys19/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RecSys 2019&lt;/a> in Copenhagen, Denmark.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>IUadaptME great success!</title><link>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2018-07-09-iuadaptme-great-success/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Jul 2018 03:48:29 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://chbeu.github.io/post/_posts_wordpress/2018-07-09-iuadaptme-great-success/</guid><description>&lt;p>Yesterday&amp;rsquo;s IUadaptME workshop at &lt;a href="https://www.um.org/umap2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UMAP 2018&lt;/a> was a great success! Thank you to all participants and my co-organizers. We had interesting discussions.&lt;/p>
